Name: High Priestess
Description: Secrets, mystery of the future, silence, tenacity, wisdom

Name: Empress
Description: Fruitfulness, Initiative, action, clandestine, the unknown

Name: Emperor
Description: Stability, power, aid, protection, a great person, conviction, reason

Name: Heirophant
Description: marriage alliance, captivity, mercy and goodness,

Name: Chariot
Description: War, triumph, succor, providence, presumption, vengeance, trouble

Name: World
Description: assured success, voyage, change of place

Name: Queen of Wands
Description: friendly, chaste, loving, honorable woman, country woman

Name: 10 of Wands
Description: oppression, who is he taking the rods to and how will they use them?

Name: 8 of Wands
Description: speed toward and end which promises felicity

Name: King of Cups
Description: fair and responsible man of law, business or divinity (the establishment)

Name: Queen of Cups
Description: good, fair, honest, devoted, someone who will do service to the querent

Name: Knight of Cups
Description: arrival, approach- sometimes that of a messenger, invitation, incitement

Name: Page of Cups
Description: fair young man, one impelled to render service and with whom the querent will be well connected,

Name: 10 of Cups
Description: contentment, repose of the entire heart

Name: 7 of Cups
Description: imagination, contemplation but without lasting attainment

Name: 5 of Cups
Description: loss, but not complete loss, inheritance, transmission

Name: 3 of Cups
Description: conclusion of a matter, victory, fulfilment

Name: Ace of Cups
Description: true heart, joy, contentment, abundance, fertility

Name: Knight of Swords
Description: wrath, war, ruin, skill bravery, capacity

Name: 5 of Swords
Description: degradation, destruction, dishonor, reversal of fortune

Name: 4 of Pentacles
Description: clinging to that which one has
